# Cloudflare Pages redirect rules.
# Replace example.com with the confirmed apex production domain before launch.
https://www.example.com/* https://example.com/:splat 301!

# Trailing-slash normalization. The Astro site uses trailingSlash: "never".
/about/ /about 301!
/our-story/ /our-story 301!
/destinations/ /destinations 301!
/contact/ /contact 301!
/blog/ /blog 301!
/blog/page/:page/ /blog/page/:page 301!
/blog/tag/:tag/ /blog/tag/:tag 301!
/blog/:slug/ /blog/:slug 301!
